Bluetooth Arduino reflow oven controller

Designed to work with the board on jimsrobot.com

The board has bluetooth which allows an Android device to upload a reflow profile.

Board specs:
 - ATTiny85 processor
 - Arduino bootloaded
 - Thermocouple amplifier for K-Type
 - Bluetooth V2
 - Digital switch input
 - Digital output for SSR
 
Directory Structure:
 \BTControl - the Arduino files
 \B4A - the basic for Android 
